			"body": "> Test Plan\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is a large UI change. As such, it would be helpful to have:\r\n- A screen recording.\r\n- Information about how this impacts accessibility. For example, the testing plan could include a section on screen reader-based testing (see [Joplin: Testing with a screen reader](https://joplinapp.org/help/dev/accessibility#testing-with-a-screen-reader)).\r\n\r\nAlso, be sure to [follow the AI policy](https://github.com/joplin/gsoc/blob/master/ai_policy.md).\r\n\r\n(Thank you for working on this!)",
